Michael Keith Spell was sentenced to 100 years prison for the murder of Sherry Arnold in 2012 . 
  He pleaded guilty in October to strangling her to death and burying her body in a shallow grave in the Bakken oil patch of Montana . 
  Co-accused Lester Van Waters was sentenced in December to 80 years in prison . 
  Sherry was a popular maths teacher in Sidney and was jogging when she was kidnapped . 
  Spell and Van Waters were under the influence of crack cocaine at the time of her murder . 
 